properties.Name: ContractDocument
properties.Description:
The documents that form a contract. 

A single contract can be formed from several documents. For instance the RFI, RFQ, ..., PO together can form a contract. A single document such as the RFI can be used as part of several documents.

Columns.Name: ContractId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Contract.

Columns.Name: DocumentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Document.

Columns.Name: ContractDocumentNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the contract document.
